=== Live Admin Warning ===
Contributors: rhlee_canonical
Tags: admin, warning
Requires at least: 2.9.2
Tested up to: 3.0.2
Stable tag: trunk

Akismet checks your comments against the Akismet web service to see if they look like spam or not.

== Description ==

A plugin to let you know you are in the admin of a live site as opposed to the admin of a test site. This is to prevent you making test changes accidentally on a live site when you were intending to make them on the test site.
